author: The Critical Drinker
description:
The more we find out about Disney Star Wars, the worse it becomes. Now apparently there were plans for a Kylo Ren movie? Not to mention the budget for Rise of Skywalker was revealed to be a shocking $600 Million. Meanwhile with Warner Bros up for sale, could James Gunn's DCU already be on the way out? Join me, MauLer, Robot Head, Vex Electronica and Erin Underwood for Open Bar Episode 161 as we find out. 

Subscribe to Robot Head: https://www.youtube.com/@robothead
Subscribe to Vex: https://www.youtube.com/@VexElectronica
Subscribe to Erin Underwood: https://www.youtube.com/@ErinUnderwood
title: Open Bar #161 - Kylo Ren's Cancelled Star Wars, Gunn's DCU In Doubt, LOTR Under Attack
